<p>Unless this relates to an SCP I'm not familiar with, I believe this should be tagged &quot;creepypasta&quot; rather than &quot;tale&quot;.</p>
<p>As for the content itself, eh. It's a sock puppet what eats teeth and blackmails you into giving it teeth out of fear that it will let (i.e. cause) Hell on Earth to happen. Maybe if I were ever afraid that the bounds of reality itself were coming unglued, I'd find the protagonist a little more relatable. As is, well, eh.</p>

