			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1648714">
									

<p>Thanks for the comment man, again much appreciated.</p>
<p>For your first question, I'm afraid, I can't tell you, it would kind of ruin the nature of my SCP, and I find it would be a lovely cliffhanger, so all I can say for now is, wait and see.</p>
<p>Why teeth? I guess I always had a kind of shiver at the thought of people collecting teeth, its one of the things I truely dread. But your question could be interpretated in another form, why does &quot;Ick&quot; collect teeth?, well, I think I hinted at why Ick collects teeth in the short story, but I drafted it so much, I might have edited it out, but if I have, then, I know people hate this but.. its a nice cliffhanger.</p>

							</div>

								
